articles.title: Verstappen describes 'worst possible outcome' for Red Bull - F1 - The Official Home of Formula 1® Racing
articles.description: Red Bull driver Max Verstappen cut a downbeat figure after a challenging first day of practice for the Monaco Grand Prix that featured set-up struggles, radio complaints and several brushes with the barriers.
